  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.1.0-beta02\" data-text=\"Version 1.1.0-beta02\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.1.0-beta02</h3>\n<p>November 3, 2021</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.compose.material:material-*:1.1.0-beta02</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/92af5b17ecee9d3c62f59e98b483e411c390f51b..f07d12061370a603549747200c79b60239706330/compose/material\">Version 1.1.0-beta02 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ripples and other indications will now only be delayed if they are inside a Modifier.scrollable() container, instead of always being delayed for a down event. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Ibefe01bcdef89e01b6e9f7edf9fe13622450f487\">Ibefe0</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/203141462\">b/203141462</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
